==過程==
===第一次宣誓===
2016年10月12日，[[香港立法會議員|香港立法會議員]]逐一進行宣誓儀式。立法會秘書長[[陳維安|陳維安]]監誓，其間表示不接納游蕙禎、梁頌恆及[[姚松炎|姚松炎]]的誓詞。
根據議事規則，三人不能參與包括[[香港立法會主席|香港立法會主席]]選舉等會議及表決，直至新任立法會大會主席為三人重新監誓<ref name="oathfk"/>為止。

[[青年新政|青年新政]]的[[游蕙禎|游蕙禎]]和[[梁頌恆|梁頌恆]]以英語宣誓時把[[中國|中國]]發音成「[[支那|支那]]」，及展示「香港不是中國」{{efn|原句[[英语|英文]]為「HONG KONG IS NOT CHINA」<ref name="oathjak">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2016/10/12/pro-democracy-hong-kong-lawmakers-defy-china-in-oath-taking.html|title=Pro-democracy Hong Kong lawmakers defy China in oath taking|publisher=[[雅加达邮报|雅加达邮报]]|date=2016-10-12|access-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013134854/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2016/10/12/pro-democracy-hong-kong-lawmakers-defy-china-in-oath-taking.html|archive-date=2016-10-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。}}的橫額<ref name="oathjak"/>，而游亦以髒話「Re-fucking」作為[[共和制|共和國]](Republic)的英語發音{{efn|游及梁把「China」一字的由原讀音「/ˈtʃaɪnə/」變為讀成「/c͡çiːnə/」，以及游疑把「Republic」一字由原讀音「/ri'pʌblək/」或「/ri'pʌblɪk/」變為讀成「Re-fucking」的讀音「/ri'fʌkɪŋ/」<ref name="oathfk">{{cite web|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161012/55763973?_ga=1.32206077.239944130.1469513308|title=【宣誓風波】游蕙禎疑講fuxking支那 姚松炎青政「加料」未被確認|publisher=[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]|date=2016-10-12|access-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012152751/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161012/55763973?_ga=1.32206077.239944130.1469513308|archive-date=2016-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="oathrafp">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.dw.com/en/new-pro-democracy-lawmakers-in-hong-kong-flaunt-opposition-to-chinese-rule/a-36022134|title=New pro-democracy lawmakers in Hong Kong flaunt opposition to Chinese rule|publisher=[[德国之声|德国之声]]|author=[[法新社|法新社]]|date=2016-10-12|access-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161015092829/http://www.dw.com/en/new-pro-democracy-lawmakers-in-hong-kong-flaunt-opposition-to-chinese-rule/a-36022134|archive-date=2016-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/10/12/asia/hong-kong-china-legco-swearing-in/index.html|title='Never imprison my mind': Hong Kong lawmakers quote Gandhi, insult China|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2016-10-12|access-